Revision history for Perl extension Plack::Middleware::XSLT

0.20002  2013-05-31
        - Fix tests on Windows
        - Document HTTP::Exception feature

0.20001  2013-05-24
        - Improve startup speed
        - Allow absolute stylesheet paths
        - Use File::Spec for path operations

0.20000  2012-08-24
        - Major rewrite
        - Use XML::LibXML::Cache for stylesheet cache

0.10003
        - Fix prereqs for Plack < 0.99

0.10002
        - Add Test::Deep to TestRequires

0.10001
        - Fix caching bug

0.10000
        - Initial release

